    <lb n="19"/>καὶ τὴν Ἀντιγόνην πάντων διὰ τῆς ἐντεύξεως ἐγκεκλημένων αὐτῆι ὑπὸ τοῦ Ἀσκλάπωνο<supplied reason="lost" cert="high">ς</supplied>, συνελ-

    <lb n="20"/>θόντα δὲ τὸν Ἀσκλάπωνα τ<unclear reason="undefined" cert="high">ῶ</unclear>ι τῆ<unclear reason="undefined" cert="high">ς</unclear> <unclear reason="undefined" cert="high">Ἀ</unclear>ν<unclear reason="undefined" cert="high">τ</unclear>ιγόνας πατρὶ Ἀλκέται εἰς Βούσιριν τοῦ Ἡρακλεοπολίτου ἕως τῆς <supplied reason="lost" cert="high">τ</supplied><unclear reason="undefined" cert="high">ριακά</unclear>δος 

    <lb n="21"/>τοῦ <unclear reason="undefined" cert="high">ἐ</unclear>νεστῶτος μη<unclear reason="undefined" cert="high">ν</unclear>ός, <supplied reason="lost" cert="high">ἐ</supplied><unclear reason="undefined" cert="high">φ</unclear>᾽ ο<unclear reason="undefined" cert="high">ὗ</unclear>, ἵ<unclear reason="undefined" cert="high">ν</unclear>α μὴ διαβάλληται ἡ <choice><corr>προγεγραμμένη</corr><sic>προγεγραμμενηι</sic></choice> δούλη Ὀπώρα ἀνακεχωρ<unclear reason="undefined" cert="high">ηκ</unclear><supplied reason="lost" cert="high">υ</supplied><unclear reason="undefined" cert="high">ῖ</unclear>α, 

    <lb n="22"/>συστήσηι περίουσαν, ε<supplied reason="lost" cert="high">ἰ δὲ μή</supplied>, ἐ<unclear reason="undefined" cert="high">κτ</unclear><supplied reason="lost" cert="high">εῖ</supplied>σαι αὐτὸν τῆι Ἀντιγόναι τὴν διατίμησιν αὐτῆς χαλκοῦ τάλαντα δέ<unclear reason="undefined" cert="high">κ</unclear><supplied reason="lost" cert="high">α</supplied> <unclear reason="undefined" cert="high">πεν</unclear>τε <num value="15"/>, 

    <lb n="23"/>ἐάν δὲ καὶ ᾖ τετελε<unclear reason="undefined" cert="high">υ</unclear><supplied reason="lost" cert="high">τηκυῖα, ἐκτεῖσαι</supplied> αὐτῆς ὁμοίως τὸν Ἀσκλάπωνα τὰ δέκα πέντε <num value="15"/> τάλαντα τοῦ χα<unclear reason="undefined" cert="high">λ</unclear><supplied reason="lost" cert="high">κοῦ</supplied> <unclear reason="undefined" cert="high">ἕ</unclear>ως 

